# ░▓▓▓███▓▒▒▒▓██████▒░░░░░░░░░▒██▒░░░░░░▓▓░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░██░░░░░░░░░▓█████▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓░
# ░▓▓▓▓▓▓███▓▓▓▓████████▒░░░▒▓▒░░░▒▓█▒░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░█▓░░░░░░░░▒███████▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓░
# ░▓▓▓▓▓▓█▓███▓▓▓█▓█████████▒░░░░▒▓▒▒▒██░░░▓█▓▓▓▓░░░░▒██▒▓▓▓▓▒░░░█████▓▓▓▓▓▓▓███▓▓▓▓▓▓░
# ░▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓█████▓▓▓▓▓▓▓█████████▓░░░░░░░▓█▒▒░░░░░░▓█▓▓▓▒░░░░░░█████▓▓▓▓▓▓▓████▓█▓▓▓▓▓▓░
# ░░░░░░░░░░▒▒▒▒▒▒░▒░▒▒░░░▒▒▒▒▒▒▓██▓░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░██▓▒▒▒▒░░▒░░▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒░░░░░░░░
.DEFAULT_GOAL = $(TARGET)

DEBUG ?= 0
ifneq ($(DEBUG),0)
CFLAGS := -ggdb -fsanitize=address
endif

NAME   := $(shell basename $$PWD)
SOURCE := $(wildcard source/*.c) rl/rl.c rl/rlm.c
OBJECT := $(addprefix object/,$(notdir $(SOURCE:.c=.o)))
HEADER := $(wildcard source/*.h) rl/rl.h rl/rlm.h

EMSCRIPTEN ?= 0

CFLAGS   += -pipe -std=gnu23 -O2 -flto=auto -Wall -Wextra -Wpedantic
CPPFLAGS := -Irl -D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=3

RENAME        := rl/rename
RENAME_FLAGS  := -g SNAKE_ -d RLAPI -p rl_

ifeq ($(EMSCRIPTEN),0)
LDFLAGS  := -lraylib -lglfw -lm
TARGET   := $(NAME)
RUN      := ./$(NAME)
else
CPPFLAGS := -Iraylib/src $(CPPFLAGS) -DPLATFORM_WEB=1
RENAME_FLAGS += -Iraylib/src
LDFLAGS  := \
        --preload-file resource \
        --shell-file raylib/src/shell.html \
        -s INITIAL_MEMORY=64MB \
        -s ALLOW_MEMORY_GROWTH=1 \
        -s STACK_SIZE=4MB \
        -s ASYNCIFY=1 \
        -s EXPORTED_RUNTIME_METHODS='["requestFullscreen"]' \
        -s USE_WEBGL2=1 \
        -s USE_GLFW=3 \
        -s EMIT_EMSCRIPTEN_METADATA=0
TARGET   := $(NAME).html
RUN      := emrun $(NAME).html
raylib raylib/src/raylib.h raylib/src/raymath.h&:
	git clone https://github.com/raysan5/raylib --depth=1

$(OBJECT): raylib/src/libraylib.web.a
rl/rl.h: raylib/src/raylib.h
rl/rlm.h: raylib/src/raymath.h

OBJECT   += raylib/src/libraylib.web.a

raylib/src/libraylib.web.a: raylib
	emmake make -c raylib/src/ PLATFORM=PLATFORM_WEB BUILD_MODE=RELEASE
endif

vpath %.c source rl
vpath %.o object

object/%.o: %.c
	$(CC) $(CFLAGS) $(CPPFLAGS) -c -o $@ $<

$(TARGET): $(HEADER) .depend | $(OBJECT)
	$(CC) $(CFLAGS) $(CPPFLAGS) -o $@ $| $(LDFLAGS)

run: $(TARGET)
	$(RUN)

rl/rl.h rl/rl.c &:
	$(RENAME) $(RENAME_FLAGS) raylib.h -o rl/rl

rl/rlm.h rl/rlm.c &:
	$(RENAME) $(RENAME_FLAGS) raymath.h -o rl/rlm

.depend: $(SOURCE)
	$(CC) $(CPPFLAGS) -MM -o $@ $+

-include .depend
